<inglise>Amendment of Code of Administrative Offences </inglise>
<eesti>Haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustikus (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1999, 41, 496; 58, 608; 92, 825; 95, 843; 2000, 10, 58; 25, 141; 28, 167; 29, 169; 40, 247; 49, 301; 49, 305; 51, 321; 54, 351; 54, 346; 54, 348; 54, 351; 55, 361; 58, 376; 84, 533; 86, 544; 86, 548; 95, 609; 95, 613; 2001, 21, 115; 21, 116; 89, 578) tehakse j&auml;rgmised muudatused ja t&auml;iendused: </eesti>
<inglise>The Code of Administrative Offences (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1999, 41, 496; 58, 608; 92, 825; 95, 843; 2000, 10, 58; 25, 141; 28, 167; 29, 169; 40, 247; 49, 301; 49, 305; 51, 321; 54, 351; 54, 346; 54, 348; 54, 351; 55, 361; 58, 376; 84, 533; 86, 544; 86, 548; 95, 609; 95, 613; 2001, 21, 115; 21, 116; 89, 578) is amended as follows: </inglise>
