<eesti>3) seadustikku t&auml;iendatakse &sect;-ga 118 (1) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>3) section 1181 is added to the Code worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"&sect; 118 (1). </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 118 (1). </inglise>
<eesti>Taksoveo korraldamine n&otilde;uetele vastava taksomeetrita </eesti>
<inglise>Organisation of taxi service without conforming taxi meter </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Taksoveo korraldamise eest mootors&otilde;idukiga, millel puudub taksomeeter v&otilde;i mille taksomeeter on rikkis, taatlemata v&otilde;i s&otilde;idukiga n&otilde;uetekohaselt kohandamata, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv viiek&uuml;mne kuni saja p&auml;evapalga ulatuses. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the organisation of taxi service with a motor vehicle which lacks a taxi meter or with a taxi meter which is broken, not collated or not adapted to the vehicle in a conforming manner: a fine of fifty up to one hundred days' wages is imposed. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Mootors&otilde;idukijuhile taksoveo eest mootors&otilde;idukiga, millel puudub taksomeeter v&otilde;i mille taksomeeter on rikkis, taatlemata v&otilde;i s&otilde;idukiga n&otilde;uetekohaselt kohandamata, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv viiek&uuml;mne kuni saja p&auml;evapalga ulatuses. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the provision of taxi service with a motor vehicle which lacks a meter or with a meter which is broken, not collated or not adapted to the vehicle in a conforming manner: a fine of fifty up to one hundred days' wages is imposed on the driver of the motor vehicle. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Taksoveol kasutataval mootors&otilde;idukil asuva taksomeetri v&otilde;i selle plommide tahtliku rikkumise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv viiek&uuml;mne kuni saja p&auml;evapalga ulatuses." </eesti>
<inglise>(3) For deliberate damaging of a meter installed on a motor vehicle or of seals affixed thereto a fine of fifty up to one hundred days' wages is imposed." </inglise>
<eesti>; </eesti>
<inglise>; </inglise>
<eesti>4) paragrahv 120 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
