<eesti>(1) Tasulise s&otilde;itjateveo korraldamise eest bussi, trammi, trollibussi v&otilde;i taksoga, millel puudub s&otilde;idukikaart, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kahesaja viiek&uuml;mne kuni kolmesaja p&auml;evapalga ulatuses v&otilde;i haldusarest kuni viisteist &ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For organisation of the carriage of passengers by a bus, tram, trolleybus or taxi which has no vehicle card a fine of two hundred and fifty up to three hundred days' wages or administrative detention for up to fifteen twenty-four hour periods is imposed. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Liiniveo korraldamise eest bussi, trammi v&otilde;i trollibussiga liiniloa v&otilde;i avaliku teenindamise lepinguta - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kahesaja viiek&uuml;mne kuni kolmesaja p&auml;evapalga ulatuses." </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the organisation of regular services by bus, tram or trolleybus without a line permit or a public service contract a fine of two hundred and fifty up to three hundred days' wages is imposed." </inglise>
