<inglise>Fee-charging carriage of passengers without vehicle card, timetable or taxi's working schedule </inglise>
<eesti>Mootors&otilde;idukijuhile tasulise s&otilde;itjateveo eest s&otilde;idukikaardi, s&otilde;iduplaani v&otilde;i valla- v&otilde;i linnavolikogu otsuse alusel sisseseatud takso t&ouml;&ouml;ajagraafikuta - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv saja kuni saja viiek&uuml;mne p&auml;evapalga ulatuses." </eesti>
<inglise>For the fee-charging carriage of passengers without a vehicle card, timetable or taxi's working schedule established pursuant to a resolution adopted by a rural municipality or city council a fine of one hundred up to one hundred and fifty days' wages is imposed on a driver of a motor vehicle." </inglise>
