<eesti>Seaduse rakendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Implementation of Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esolev seadus j&otilde;ustub 2000. aasta 1. oktoobril. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) This Act enters into force on 1 October 2000. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Vedaja suhtes, kes korraldab tasulist s&otilde;itjatevedu maanteeliikluses enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kehtinud n&otilde;uete kohaselt s&otilde;lmitud lepingu v&otilde;i v&auml;ljaantud loa alusel, kohaldatakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse 8. peat&uuml;ki s&auml;tteid alates 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarist, v&auml;lja arvatud k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 45 ja &sect; 46 l&otilde;iked 2, 5 ja 6, mida kohaldatakse 2001. aasta 1. m&auml;rtsist. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The provisions of Chapter 8 of this Act apply to carriers who organise fee-charging carriage of passengers on the basis of a contract entered into or licence issued pursuant to the requirements in force prior to entry into force of this Act as of 1 January 2002, except &sect; 45 and subsections 46 (2), (5) and (6) of this Act which apply as of 1 March 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(07.02.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.03.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 85) </eesti>
<inglise>(07.02.2001 entered into force 01.03.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 85) </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Rahvusvahelise autoveo tegevusluba ja taksoveo tegutsemisluba, mis on vedajale antud enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kehtinud n&otilde;uete kohaselt, kehtib loal m&auml;rgitud kehtivusaja l&otilde;puni, kuid mitte kauem kui 2001. aasta 31. detsembrini. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Licences for the international carriage by vehicle and operating licences for taxi services granted to a carrier pursuant to the requirements in force prior to the entry into force of this Act are valid until the expiry date indicated on the licence, however, for not longer than until 31 December 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(07.02.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.03.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 85) </eesti>
<inglise>(07.02.2001 entered into force 01.03.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 85) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Vedude eest vastutav isik, kes on k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumiseni tegelnud rahvusvahelise s&otilde;itjateveoga, peab vastama seaduses s&auml;testatud p&auml;devusn&otilde;uetele alates 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarist. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Persons responsible for transport operation who until the entry into force of this Act have engaged in the international carriage of passengers shall comply with the professional competence requirement provided for in this Act as of 1 January 2003. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist bussi-, trammi- v&otilde;i trollibussiveoks antud liiniluba, mille kehtivus l&otilde;peb enne 2002. aasta 1. jaanuari, kehtib liiniloale m&auml;rgitud ajani. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) Line permits granted for carriage by bus, tram or trolleybus prior to the entry into force of this Act which expire before 1 January 2002 are valid until the expiry date indicated on the line permit. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Bussi-, trammi- v&otilde;i trollibussiveoks vedajale enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kehtinud n&otilde;uete kohaselt antud liiniluba, mille kehtivus l&otilde;peb p&auml;rast 2001. aasta 31. detsembrit, kehtib liiniloale m&auml;rgitud ajani tingimusel, et vedaja on saanud k&auml;esoleva seaduse 8. peat&uuml;ki s&auml;tete kohaselt 2001. aasta 31. detsembriks &uuml;histranspordiloa. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) Line permits for carriage by bus, tram or trolleybus granted to carriers pursuant to the requirements in force prior to the entry into force of this Act which expire after 31 December 2001 are valid until the expiry date indicated on the line permit on condition that the carrier has obtained a public transport licence pursuant to the provisions of Chapter 8 of this Act by 31 December 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(07.02.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.03.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 85) </eesti>
<inglise>(07.02.2001 entered into force 01.03.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 85) </inglise>
<eesti>(7) K&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumiseni kehtinud n&otilde;uete kohaselt antud rahvusvahelise autoveo tegevusloa alusel rahvusvahelist s&otilde;itjatevedu, liiniloa alusel bussi-, trammi- v&otilde;i trollibussivedu, samuti tegutsemisloa alusel taksovedu korraldanud vedaja v&otilde;ib aegunud rahvusvahelise autoveo tegevusloa asemele taotleda &uuml;histranspordiluba, aegunud liiniloa asemele uut liiniluba v&otilde;i liiniluba veo korraldamiseks muul liinil, samuti taksoveo aegunud tegutsemisloa asemele taksoveoluba alates 2001. aasta 1. m&auml;rtsist &uuml;ksnes k&auml;esoleva seaduse 8. peat&uuml;ki s&auml;tete alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) A carrier who organised international carriage of passengers on the basis of an activity licence for international road transport issued pursuant to the requirements in force prior to entry into force of this Act, carriage by bus, tram or trolleybus on the basis of a line permit or a taxi service on the basis of an operating licence may apply for a public transport licence to replace the expired activity licence for international road transport, for a new line permit or a line permit to organise transport operations on another line to replace the expired line permit and for a taxi licence to replace the expired operating licence for a taxi service as of 1 March 2001 only on the basis of the provisions of Chapter 8 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>Vedaja suhtes kohaldatakse &uuml;histranspordiloa, liiniloa v&otilde;i taksoveoloa v&auml;ljaandmisest alates 8. peat&uuml;ki k&otilde;iki s&auml;tteid. </eesti>
<inglise>As of the issue of a public transport licence, line permit or taxi licence, all provisions of Chapter 8 shall apply to the carrier. </inglise>
<eesti>(07.02.2001 j&otilde;ust.01.03.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 85) </eesti>
<inglise>(07.02.2001 entered into force 01.03.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 85) </inglise>
<eesti>(8) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 5-7 nimetatud liiniloa kehtimise kohta esitatavad n&otilde;uded kehtivad ka avaliku liiniveo lepingu kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) The requirements for the validity of line permits provided in subsections (5) -(7) of this section also apply to public regular services contracts. </inglise>
<eesti>(9) &Uuml;histranspordiloa alusel s&otilde;idukikaardi andmise korral kohaldatakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 36 l&otilde;ikes 3 etten&auml;htud omavahendite suuruse n&otilde;uet: </eesti>
<inglise>(9) The requirement concerning the amount of own funds prescribed in subsection 36 (3) of this Act in the case of the grant of public transport licences shall be implemented: </inglise>
<eesti>1) rahvusvahelist vedu korraldavale vedajale: </eesti>
<inglise>1) with regard to carriers organising international transport operations: </inglise>
<eesti>- alates 2001. aasta 1. jaanuarist - 30 protsenti &sect; 36 l&otilde;ikes 3 etten&auml;htud suurusest; </eesti>
<inglise>as of 1 January 2001 - to the extent of 30 per cent of the amount prescribed in subsection 36 (3) of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>- alates 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarist - 100 protsenti &sect; 36 l&otilde;ikes 3 etten&auml;htud suurusest; </eesti>
<inglise>as of 1 January 2002 - to the extent of 100 per cent of the amount prescribed in subsection 36 (3) of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>2) siseriiklikku vedu korraldavale vedajale: </eesti>
<inglise>2) with regard to carriers organising domestic transport operations: </inglise>
<eesti>- alates 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarist - 50 protsenti &sect; 36 l&otilde;ikes 3 etten&auml;htud suurusest; </eesti>
<inglise>as of 1 January 2002 - to the extent of 50 per cent of the amount prescribed in subsection 36 (3) of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>- alates 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarist - 100 protsenti &sect; 36 l&otilde;ikes 3 etten&auml;htud suurusest. </eesti>
<inglise>as of 1 January 2003 - to the extent of 100 per cent of the amount prescribed in subsection 36 (3) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(10) Vedaja suhtes, kes on alustanud taksoveo korraldamist enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist, kohaldatakse seaduse &sect; 24 l&otilde;ike 3 punktides 1 ja 3 s&auml;testatud n&otilde;udeid printeri olemasolu v&otilde;i taksoteenuste tariifide &uuml;ksnes automaatse &uuml;mberl&uuml;litamise kohta alates 2001. aasta 1. juulist. </eesti>
<inglise>(10) The requirements provided for in clauses 24 (3) 1) and 3) of this Act concerning the existence of a printer or the requirement that the tariffs for taxi service switch strictly automatically shall be imposed with regard to carriers who have commenced the organisation of taxi service prior to the entry into force of this Act as of 1 July 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>Kuni selle ajani peab taksojuht printeri puudumisel takso kasutaja n&otilde;udmisel v&auml;ljastama temale vedaja rekvisiitidega blanketil k&auml;sitsi t&auml;idetud kviitungi osutatud taksoteenuse kuup&auml;eva, kellaaja ja maksumuse kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>Until such time, a taxi driver shall provide the user of the taxi with a receipt filled out by hand on a form bearing requisite information concerning the carrier which sets out the date, time and total cost of the provided taxi service. (1) RT = Riigi Teataja = State Gazette </inglise>

